<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head><meta charset="UTF-8"/><title>Host App</title></head>
  <body style="font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;max-width:640px;margin:2rem auto;padding:0 1rem">
    <h1>The host app</h1>
    <p>The panel below is a separate remote app that fetches its data before rendering — watch it stream in.</p>
    <micro-frame src="http://localhost:3001/fragment" client-reorder timeout=0>
      <@loading>Contacting the remote…</@loading>
      <@catch|err|>The remote is unavailable: ${err.message}</@catch>
    </micro-frame>
  </body>
</html>
